{
  "id": "adv_event_2504_02_04",
  "title": "裏切り者は誰だ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――時空の狭間が閉じるまであと6時間",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—6 Hours Until the Space-Time Rift Closes",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 2.2666667223,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_watch-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_telepathy-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3400.0000556
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "ビビビビビー！　こちらさくら！\nついに『時空エネルギー』が手に入りました～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Bibibibibi―! This is Sakura!\nWe finally obtained the “Space-Time Energy”~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.4000000556,
      "endTime": 10.2454867284,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "zikuu",
      "startTime": 11.3788209518
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "ついにパラレルトラベルマシン修理完了よ！\nこれで脱出出来るわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The Parallel Travel Machine is finally fully repaired!\nNow we can escape!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.4788204432,
      "endTime": 18.2224034547,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "zikuu",
      "startTime": 18.4224036455
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "さくら、遙子さん、みんな……！\nついに……ついに星見プロに帰って来れるんだな！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura‚ Haruko-san‚ everyone…!\nAt last… you can finally return to Hoshimi Pro!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.4224036455,
      "endTime": 26.6832653284,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "zikuu",
      "startTime": 26.89659849
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "一時はどうなるかと思ったけれど\n{user}さんとバルゴさんのおかげよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For a moment I wondered how things would turn out‚ but\nit’s all thanks to you and Barugo-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.89659849,
      "endTime": 32.7201361258,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "zikuu",
      "startTime": 32.9268025636
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "さっさと帰るよ。こっちスマホも使えないし\nSNSも更新出来ないから最悪！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s hurry back. I can’t even use my phone here‚\nand I can’t update my socials either—this is the worst!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.9268025636,
      "endTime": 39.8412015199,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_switch-01.m4a",
          "delay": 16006.530245200003
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "zikuu",
      "startTime": 40.0412014245
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "ファンのみなさん、待っていてくださいまし！\nよーし、行きますわよ！　スイッチオンですわ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone‚ dear fans‚ please wait for us!\nAll right‚ here we go! Switching it on~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.0412014245,
      "endTime": 48.966666142200005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "zikuu",
      "startTime": 49.5623097339
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "……あれ？　マシンが起動しない……\n一体どういうこと！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh? The machine won’t start…\nWhat on earth is going on!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.5623097339,
      "endTime": 56.6577973285,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "バルゴ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Barugo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと待った星見のアイドル！\nパラレルトラベルマシン起動のカギは！　ぎょ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hold on‚ Hoshimi idols!\nThe key to activating the Parallel Travel Machine is—gyo…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.6777930337,
      "endTime": 63.2154803353,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_spacetimegap-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "zikuu",
      "startTime": 63.2444599548
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zagura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "ゲーシゲシゲシ！　かかったなゲシな！\nやはりバルゴ、裏切者はお前だったゲシか……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Gee-shi geshi geshi! Gotcha‚ geshi!\nSo it was you after all‚ Barugo—the traitor‚ geshi…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.2444599548,
      "endTime": 71.97779227080001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "なっ……ザグラ達、お前達はガナを吊るし上げていた\nはずじゃ！？　なぜテレパシーに割り込めるんだ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wha… Zagura‚ weren’t you all busy hanging Gana up\njust now!? How are you interfering with our telepathy!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.2111250955,
      "endTime": 81.85824538050001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "ズミレ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "ザグラ様の指示で、ガナに一芝居打ってもらってん\nまんまとかかってくれたなぁ、あんちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "On Lady Zagura’s orders‚ we had Gana put on a little act.\nAnd you fell for it perfectly‚ didn’t ya‚ bro?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.0715784469,
      "endTime": 90.95158313900001,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_telepathy-01.m4a",
          "delay": 18428.421553099994
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zagura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "ゲシゲシゲシ……私も川咲さくらならぬガワザギ\nザグラ……テレパシーは習得済みゲシ！　ビビビビー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Geshi geshi geshi… I too—Kawasaki Sakura… no—\nGawazagi Zagura… have mastered telepathy‚ geshi! Bibibibi―!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.1382496911,
      "endTime": 102.2666666508,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "ズズ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zuzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "ウラギリモノ……ユルサナイ\nオデ、バルゴ、コブシデタオス……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Traitor… unforgivable.\nMe… beat Barugo… with fists…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.4049209354,
      "endTime": 111.6315895793,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-01.m4a",
          "delay": 21728.412382100003
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "こ、これが……私！？　そんな……私はこんな\n無骨な怪物みたいな話し方じゃ……ありませんわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Th-this is… me!? No… I don’t speak\nlike some rough‚ brutish monster…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.8382563033,
      "endTime": 124.1999999841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "きゃー！　す、すずがショックで倒れちゃった！\nあなた達、なんてことを……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kya―! S-Suzu fainted from the shock!\nHow could you do such a thing…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.7191805599,
      "endTime": 130.5691759823,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "ゴドノ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Godono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "君がパラレルワールドの私か……フフ、君も私のように\n美しく、優雅に振る舞いたまえよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So you are my counterpart from a parallel world… fufu.\nTry to conduct yourself beautifully and elegantly‚ like me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.7625093537,
      "endTime": 141.2282022316,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "うるさい！　私達をこんな目に遭わせたこと\n絶対に許さないんだから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shut up! For putting us through all this‚\nI’ll never forgive you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.2925080059,
      "endTime": 147.4218727825,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zagura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "いくらわめいてもお前らの負けゲシ！　さぁバルゴ！\nいい子ぶってもお前もBIG4になりたいんだろゲシ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Scream all you want—you’ve already lost‚ geshi! Now‚ Barugo!\nYou can play nice all you want‚ but you want to become one of the BIG 4 too‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.6085394301,
      "endTime": 157.2351991095,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "ザグラ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Zagura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "一緒にBIG4になって念願の\nトップアイドルになるゲシ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's join the BIG 4‚ and finally become the top idols\nwe’ve always dreamed of‚ geshi!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.4418656426,
      "endTime": 162.1885373669,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "バルゴ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Barugo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "……まだ負けてないYO星見プロ！\nマシン動かすヒント『展示スペース』に隠したYOYO",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You haven’t lost yet‚ Hoshimi Pro‚ YO!\nI hid the hint to start the machine in the “Exhibition Space‚” YOYO!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.6751918551,
      "endTime": 173.2552011248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "バルゴ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Barugo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "ザグラは私が食い止める！　私を置いて早く行け\nマネージャー！　俺の屍を越えてゆけサクリファイス！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll hold Zagura off! Leave me and go—hurry!\nManager! Cross over my fallen body—sacrifice!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.4418676771,
      "endTime": 181.6218706526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "バルゴさん、もうバレてるし直接教えてくれても……！\nいや……あなたの想い、受け取りました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Barugo-san‚ they’ve already found out‚ so you could just tell us directly…!\nNo… I understand your feelings!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.8085373955,
      "endTime": 189.24853726199999,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 12792.11935219999
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_02_04-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、『展示スペース』のヒントを探しに行くから\n俺の指示通りに動いてくれ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone‚ we’re going to search for the hint in the “Exhibition Space‚”\nso follow my instructions!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.4552040813,
      "endTime": 195.02513587459998,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}